Hydrogen&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;simplest&nbsp;element&nbsp;It&nbsp;seems&nbsp;to&nbsp;have&nbsp;only<br>
two&nbsp;components,&nbsp;a&nbsp;proton,&nbsp;which&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;positive&nbsp;charge,&nbsp;and<br>
