ber&nbsp;of&nbsp;them),&nbsp;contains&nbsp;up&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;certain&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;electrons,&nbsp;but<br>no&nbsp;more<br>
