chunks&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;high-frequency&nbsp;light,&nbsp;like&nbsp;violet&nbsp;This&nbsp;explains<br>why&nbsp;hot&nbsp;objects&nbsp;radiate&nbsp;energy&nbsp;as&nbsp;they&nbsp;do<br>
