ited&nbsp;to&nbsp;three&nbsp;dimensions&nbsp;Nontheless,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;mathematics<br>of&nbsp;the&nbsp;situation<br>
The&nbsp;point&nbsp;to&nbsp;think&nbsp;about&nbsp;is&nbsp;that&nbsp;when&nbsp;we&nbsp;make&nbsp;a&nbsp;measure-<br>
