WHAT&nbsp;HAPPENS&nbsp;/&nbsp;85<br>
in&nbsp;this&nbsp;branch&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;universe&nbsp;(I&nbsp;run&nbsp;up&nbsp;the&nbsp;stairs)&nbsp;The&nbsp;other<br>
