<b>statistical&nbsp;pattein&nbsp;i&nbsp;c&nbsp;mttrfeience&nbsp;However&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;words&nbsp;of&nbsp;Paul&nbsp;Dirac<br>(another&nbsp;founder&nbsp;ot&nbsp;quantum&nbsp;mechanics)</b><br>
