calculate&nbsp;from&nbsp;them,&nbsp;what&nbsp;probabilities&nbsp;are&nbsp;associated&nbsp;with<br>what&nbsp;initial&nbsp;conditions&nbsp;Using&nbsp;this&nbsp;method,&nbsp;which&nbsp;Heisenberg<br>called&nbsp;matrix&nbsp;mechanics,&nbsp;we&nbsp;deal&nbsp;only&nbsp;with&nbsp;physical&nbsp;observa-<br>
