mathematics&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;phvsics,&nbsp;his&nbsp;next&nbsp;discovery&nbsp;shook<br>the&nbsp;very&nbsp;foundations&nbsp;&nbsp;o&nbsp;f&nbsp;'&nbsp;the&nbsp;exact&nbsp;sciences&nbsp;'&nbsp;He&nbsp;proved&nbsp;that,<br>
