electrons,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;way&nbsp;that&nbsp;long&nbsp;sea&nbsp;waves&nbsp;barely&nbsp;are<br>influenced&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;thin&nbsp;pole&nbsp;sticking&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;water<br>
