&quot;ultimate,&nbsp;irreducible&nbsp;realities&quot;3&nbsp;in&nbsp;themselves&nbsp;Henceforth,<br>as&nbsp;in&nbsp;Cjuantum&nbsp;mechanics,&nbsp;there&nbsp;would&nbsp;be&nbsp;no&nbsp;concrete&nbsp;im-<br>agery&nbsp;associated&nbsp;with&nbsp;physical&nbsp;theor\<br>
