(the&nbsp;principle&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;constancy&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;velocity&nbsp;of&nbsp;light&nbsp;and&nbsp;the<br>principle&nbsp;of&nbsp;relativity)&nbsp;First,&nbsp;a&nbsp;moving&nbsp;object&nbsp;appears&nbsp;to<br>
