stationary,&nbsp;is&nbsp;their<i>&nbsp;proper</i>&nbsp;length&nbsp;and<i>&nbsp;proper</i>&nbsp;time&nbsp;(&quot;Proper&quot;<br>means&nbsp;&quot;one&nbsp;s&nbsp;own&nbsp;')&nbsp;Proper&nbsp;lengths&nbsp;and&nbsp;proper&nbsp;times&nbsp;always<br>appear&nbsp;normal&nbsp;What&nbsp;we&nbsp;see&nbsp;if&nbsp;we&nbsp;are&nbsp;stationary&nbsp;and&nbsp;observe<br>
