the&nbsp;predicament&nbsp;back&nbsp;on&nbsp;earth&nbsp;As&nbsp;far&nbsp;as&nbsp;we&nbsp;are&nbsp;concerned,<br>everything&nbsp;is&nbsp;proceeding&nbsp;according&nbsp;to&nbsp;plan,&nbsp;although&nbsp;we&nbsp;are<br>becoming&nbsp;bored&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;routine&nbsp;of&nbsp;pressing&nbsp;a&nbsp;button&nbsp;every<br>
