phenomena&nbsp;inside&nbsp;the&nbsp;elevator&nbsp;They&nbsp;are&nbsp;in&nbsp;an&nbsp;mertial&nbsp;co-<br>ordinate&nbsp;system,&nbsp;and&nbsp;they&nbsp;can&nbsp;prove&nbsp;it&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;laws&nbsp;of<br>mechanics<br>
