its&nbsp;own&nbsp;magnitude&nbsp;Closer&nbsp;than&nbsp;that,&nbsp;however,&nbsp;and&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;com-<br>pletely&nbsp;overpowered&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;strong&nbsp;force<br>
Yukawa&nbsp;decided&nbsp;to&nbsp;explain&nbsp;this&nbsp;powerful&nbsp;but&nbsp;very&nbsp;short-<br>
