geneous&nbsp;is&nbsp;another&nbsp;example&nbsp;These&nbsp;symmetries&nbsp;simply&nbsp;mean<br>that&nbsp;a&nbsp;physics&nbsp;experiment&nbsp;performed&nbsp;in&nbsp;Boston&nbsp;this&nbsp;spring&nbsp;will<br>give&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;result&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;experiment&nbsp;performed&nbsp;in<br>
