256&nbsp;/&nbsp;ENLIGHTENMENT<br>
everything—all&nbsp;the&nbsp;separate&nbsp;parts&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;universe—are&nbsp;mani-<br>festations&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;whole&nbsp;There&nbsp;is&nbsp;only<i>&nbsp;one</i>&nbsp;reality,&nbsp;and&nbsp;it<br>is&nbsp;whole&nbsp;and&nbsp;unified&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;one<br>
