is&nbsp;indescribable&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;common&nbsp;misconception&nbsp;(hterallv)&nbsp;to<br>mistake&nbsp;the&nbsp;description&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;state&nbsp;of&nbsp;being&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;state&nbsp;itself<br>For&nbsp;example,&nbsp;try&nbsp;to&nbsp;describe&nbsp;happiness&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;impossible&nbsp;We<br>
