adoxical&nbsp;puzzles&nbsp;of&nbsp;quantum&nbsp;phenomena&nbsp;took&nbsp;him&nbsp;far&nbsp;bevond<br>the&nbsp;boundaries&nbsp;of&nbsp;physics&nbsp;This&nbsp;brief&nbsp;work&nbsp;pointed&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;fusion<br>of&nbsp;ontology&nbsp;epistemologv&nbsp;and&nbsp;psychology&nbsp;which&nbsp;only&nbsp;now&nbsp;is<br>
